  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nigeria - Naira line of credit to FirstRand Bank subsidiary, Rand Merchant Bank Nigeria Limited</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">La pr&#xE9;sente intervention concerne la ligne de cr&#xE9;dit Naira &#xE0; la filiale de FirstRand Bank, Rand Merchant Bank Nigeria Limited. Elle vise &#xE0; fournir une ligne de cr&#xE9;dit multidevises &#xE0; moyen terme d&apos;un montant maximum de 300 millions USD &#xE0; FirstRand Bank Limited, filiale &#xE0; 100 % de la soci&#xE9;t&#xE9; sud-africaine FirstRand Limited. Le produit de la Facilit&#xE9; servira &#xE0; financer des projets dans un certain nombre de secteurs et dans un certain nombre de pays africains.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The present intervention concerns the Naira line of credit to FirstRand Bank subsidiary, Rand Merchant Bank Nigeria Limited. It aims to provide a medium-term, multi-currency line of credit of up to the equivalent of USD 300 million to FirstRand Bank Limited, which is a wholly-owned subsidiary of the South Africa based FirstRand Limited. The proceeds of the Facility will be used for funding projects in a number of sectors and across a number of African countries.</narrative>
  </description>
